'''''Agoniates''''' is genus of characiform fishes from [[tropical]] [[South America]].
==Species== There are currently two recognized species in this genus:<ref>{{FishBase genus | genus = Agoniates| month = April | year = 2013}}</ref> * ''[[Agoniates anchovia]]'' <small>[[Carl H. Eigenmann|C. H. Eigenmann]], 1914</small> * ''[[Agoniates halecinus]]'' <small>[[Johannes Peter Müller|J. P. Müller]] & [[Franz Hermann Troschel|Troschel]], 1845</small>
